title: Secret Warriors, Vol. 2: God of Fear, God of War
description: Baron Strucker and Norman Osborn team up to drive out the Marvel Universe's ultimate covert superteam. It's wall-to-wall insanity as the Dark Avengers and the Thunderbolts go after the Secret Warriors. It's time for Ares to get his son back!Collecting: Secret Warriors 7-10, Dark Reign: The List Secret Warriors
author: Jonathan Hickman
